Cross-Engine Dependencies
FLO integrates with but does not own:
DAT — execution outcomes
GGP — audit and governance
SIM — scenario financial modeling
MUX — external payment rails

Completion Criteria
FLO documentation is complete when:
NS-FLO-000 → NS-FLO-014 exist
Financial truth is singular and auditable
No execution or governance logic leaks into FLO

